Class ReconcilableTransaction

java.lang.Object
  transaction.ReconcilableTransaction
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
AtmWithdrawalTransaction, CashPurchaseTransaction
public abstract class ReconcilableTransaction
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<ReconcilableTransaction>

Defines the fields and methods used to manage a transaction object for reconciliation. Contains Comparable implementation to allow sorting of ReconcilableTransaction based on date and transaction id.
